'''Faissol Fahad Bolade Gnonlonfin''' (wavutse 1985) n'umuyobozi wa firime akaba  n'umu producer<ref>Fahad Boladé Gnonlonfin Faissol in Bordeaux | Moneyhouse <nowiki>https://www.moneyhouse.ch</nowiki> › list › person › gnonlonfi...</ref>.

Mu mwaka wa 2012, Gnonlonfin yakoze ifoto ye ya mbere, ''Obalé le chasseur'', agaragaza umuturage wo muri Bénine winjiye mu itsinda ry’abahigi<ref>Faissol Fahad Boladé Gnonlonfin - CinéLounge <nowiki>https://www.cinelounge.org</nowiki> › Perso</ref>. Yize kuriyi ngingo imyaka ibiri kandi yitegereza impaka hagati yabahiga gakondo nabashinzwe kubungabunga inyamaswa<ref name=":0">Faissol Gnonlonfin - Beninese film director and producer (born ... <nowiki>https://thenotablepeople.com</nowiki> › profile › Faissol_Gnonlo...</ref>.  Nk’uko uwahoze ari umwarimu Jean-François Hautin abitangaza ngo umuzungu ntabwo yashoboraga gufata amashusho neza umuhango w'abahiga<ref>Faissol Gnonlonfin - Fiche Personne sur Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › personnes</ref>. Filime ya kabiri ya Gnonlonfin ''Ni ici ni ailleur'' isuzuma icyerekezo cyo kurwanya ikoreshwa rya gaze ya shale muri Ardèche, ikayihuza no gukuramo umutungo muri [[Afurika]]<ref>Faissol Gnonlonfin - Africiné <nowiki>http://www.africine.org</nowiki> › person</ref>. 

Nyuma yo kwibanda ku documentaire, inyinshi muri zo zabonye ibihembo, Gnonlonfin yatangiye gukora ibihimbano mu 2014. Muri 2017, yakoranye na Berni Goldblat hamwe na sosiyete ikora Les Lesms du Djabadjah kuri ''Wallay''<ref>Benin: Faissol Fahad Gnonlonfin, image pioneer - Young ... <nowiki>https://www.jeuneafrique.com</nowiki> › company</ref> .  Yasohowe cyane, itorwa mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Carthage 2017<ref>CineSud 2015: Faissol Fahad Gnonlonfin talks about cinema ... <nowiki>https://blog.courrierinternational.com</nowiki> › ...</ref>.  Muri Werurwe 2018, Gnonlonfin yayoboye amahugurwa yo gutunganya amashusho muri [[Burukina Faso|Burkinafaso]].<ref>Images francophones</ref> Gnonlonfin yashinze isosiyete ikora Merveilles Production kugirango ishishikarize abakora firime. Yibera cyane mubufaransa ariko amara hafi amezi abiri mumwaka muri Bénin<ref name=":0" />. 
